# Financial Analysis Dashboard

## Overview

An interactive Power BI dashboard designed to analyze financial transactions, customer segments, taxes, fees, and transaction performance.

## Tools Used

- Power BI
- DAX
- Power Query
- Excel (Data Source)

## Dashboard Features

- KPI Cards
- Monthly Trend Analysis
- Customer Segment Analysis
- Transaction Status
- State-wise Analysis
- Gender Analysis
- Dynamic Slicers

## KPIs

- Total Amount
- Total Transactions
- Average Transaction Value
- Total Fees
- Total Tax

## Skills Demonstrated

- Data Modeling
- Power Query Transformations
- DAX Measures
- Interactive Dashboard Design
- Conditional Formatting
- Slicers & Filters
